name: Swimmers
target: Full Body, Upper Body, Core, Lower Body
target_muscles: Shoulders, Back, Lower Back, Glutes, Hamstrings
instruction: Lie on your belly with your arms and legs fully extended. Raise both arms and legs off the mat and lift your head and chest. Flutter your arms and legs and keep alternating sides for the entire duration of the set.
hints: Keep your arms and legs fully extended, maintain a neutral spine and elongate your body. Breathe slowly, pull your abs in, keep your core muscles tight, and maintain your hips and upper body stable.
